{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ResizeObserver.unobserve()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/unobserve","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Resize_Observer_API\">Resize Observer API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver\"><code>ResizeObserver</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/ResizeObserver\"><code>ResizeObserver()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/disconnect\"><code>disconnect()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/observe\"><code>observe()</code></a></li><li><em><code>unobserve()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Resize Observer API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserverEntry\"><code>ResizeObserverEntry</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div></div>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>unobserve()</code></strong> method of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver\"><code>ResizeObserver</code></a> interface ends the observing of a specified <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> or <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code></a>.<br>\n <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver\"><code>ResizeObserver</code></a> 接口的&nbsp;<strong><code>unobserve()</code></strong>&nbsp; 方法用于结束一个指定的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> 或&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code></a> 的观察。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">void unobserve(target);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"target\">target</dt>\n <dd>取消监听的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> 或&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code></a> 的引用。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"异常","title":"异常","isH3":true,"content":"<p>无。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/resize-observer/#dom-resizeobserver-unobserve","title":"Resize Observer"}],"query":"api.ResizeObserver.unobserve"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.ResizeObserver.unobserve","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/unobserve/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"The unobserve() method of the ResizeObserver interface ends the observing of a specified Element or SVGElement.\n ResizeObserver 接口的 unobserve()  方法用于结束一个指定的 Element 或 SVGElement 的观察。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ResizeObserver.unobserve()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ResizeObserver.unobserve()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/resizeobserver/unobserve","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/transl